Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那兩人是在何種狀況下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}進行著何種對話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}甚至連我自己的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不曾了解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學…姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 這個是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但僅僅是看著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就感到無比難受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月…學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.39,0:00:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對於面對自己的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很是畏懼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 害羞鬼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說…我為什麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}跑到這兒應該就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 那女生也太強硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:02:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要說！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了 請你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說…說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再不快點 會被檸檬學姐罵的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要回房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總算回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們倆 究竟去幹嘛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人老師教了我一些演技的訣竅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}老師可是完美主義者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是些小事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比起這個…學姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有啥事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實…沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說比起這個…一夏學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}攝影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}準備 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 你就死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽…聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你可是罪犯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樹下她…突然就哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}無論怎樣…都不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}要是錢我多少還是有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐突然就出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一無所知的我 膠片還在運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}這…這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}啊 UFO！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像…有些尷尬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}在哪在哪 在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}那裡那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣下去可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}哪裡！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我這麼想著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}有破綻！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了 放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那你就回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是為什麼 來到這個星球的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有…還有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有真正的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你喜歡小海嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你…你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才這個景 換個角度再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川 麻煩你拿一下包包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻 換地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嚇到你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐也來幫忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我現在正與電影之神進行電波交流
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 千春？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真刺激呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(642,664)}aggressive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是叫有澤…來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那女生挺可愛的 哲朗和她交往算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這種話…可不能對哲朗說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無論如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}北原同學 你能代替他拿下反光板嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍攝 要繼續了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要拍得可愛點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到這裡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗一去不復返
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻千載空悠悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏學姐也不在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海…海人 你在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 不在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學他 剛才悄悄走出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去樹下同學那裡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人他…果然對樹下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼能這麼斷定？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看就…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…不介意的話能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…心意是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 讓我們好好談談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:52.37,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}活力飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:08:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}703號室的樹下小姐現在外出不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請問是叫霧島先生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有樹下小姐給您的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請等等~哲朗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說都跑了幾小時了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她是鐵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請等等我~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 這麼害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗先生你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又被你救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝啊 美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幫我保密的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你…你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是溫柔呢 哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還行吧 不過只限於對可愛的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好過分啊 哲朗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}東躲西藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然我也不討厭這樣的Play就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來 我們繼續享受約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}至…至今為止的那算是約會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}把人家叫出來還遲到 然後沉默不語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 我還沒整理好自己的思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…我有事想好好問問你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:10:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…樹下同學對海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…是怎麼看的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果我這麼說的話 你會怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在戲弄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉 因為有點羨慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說你在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.09,0:10:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我覺得哲朗感到很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼會覺得困擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對吧 哲朗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了 你喜歡哲朗先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這種…明明就是個暴露狂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你跑進來的時候沒有穿內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這很奇怪吧 很奇怪不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不穿內褲到處走 想像著被別人看到而感到興奮的變態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被這種女孩子喜歡哲朗也不願意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}裸族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是…裸族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被 被甩了是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被海人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是啦 是被在東京的學校裡的學長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來沖繩是為了心碎旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.47,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}日文寫作傷心旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後就碰巧再會小海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和大家一起鬧鬧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想借此掩蓋掉被男朋友甩掉後寂寞的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為這樣…給你們添了不少麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼你那時候會哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和被男朋友甩掉時所說的完全相同的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從小海口中說了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回想起了往事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不經意間就哭了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時 小海這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他說「我有喜歡的人了」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想 那一定是在說你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在說什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看小海那樣我就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再怎麼說 我和他姑且也是青梅竹馬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你心裡也是一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 這算賠罪咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樹下同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天的拍攝也請多關照囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}賠罪是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是被樹下叫過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 為什麼學姐會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 明白什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一定 已經明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 差不多該告訴我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢 如果你能穿上這件衣服的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:39.19,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}導演你是不是錯過了很重要的一段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？還要穿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}裸族？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…裸族是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那種…在家裡都是過著全裸自在生活的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 家人也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我從小也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我以為在家裡都這樣所以就是理所當然的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}上小學後就開始覺得有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是這種事又不能對誰說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道穿內衣是理所當然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是我有很嚴重的低血壓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}偶爾會忘了穿內衣就這麼去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太羞人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道這樣下去可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘗試矯正了很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是偶爾還是會犯這毛病…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我想那就不要引人注目就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就讓自己變得透明起來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是面對這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜還是來和我搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗和霧島同學也願意做我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我實在…太高興了…太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才不想被你們知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:15:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不是變態…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}經常忘記的話把替換衣物預先放進包裡不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後裝作去上廁所把它穿上就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}體操服什麼的還是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}慌個手忙腳亂也解決不了問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼叫變得透明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太過消極思考了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有煩惱就找我商量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜也是 海也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果被大家討厭了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才不會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你信不過我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以呢 有什麼想說的就說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樹下她 有過這樣的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她說「對不起」了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊啊 我真沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明已經察覺到她在勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}卻沒有好好聽她訴說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結果變成「交給學姐」這種形式解決
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想樹下同學她其實是想對海人你訴說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我先一步把她叫了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}把樹下？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 所以白天的時候你才會在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你有什麼話要對她說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總覺得啊 那兩個人間的氣氛很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反而我倒成了電燈泡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗先生明明說過沒有喜歡的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我這樣到底是多像個小丑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明只是來陪我的碎心旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}結果大家都一樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貨真價實的天然…太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}害我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真傷腦筋吶 這個夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}天色晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他們在擔心了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才的答復 不用說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣同學他怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說不定現在還被和樹下一起的那個女孩糾纏著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然 被女孩子那樣猛追的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作為男生不會動什麼歪腦筋嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔 多少有點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樹下同學那時候也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別欺負我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我並不想被追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而是想去追別人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想去追我喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…如果我的心意讓學姐感到困擾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我沒有…感到困擾喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…行…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們在做什麼喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.55,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}救護車！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷谷谷 谷川同學！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊啊 我們什麼都沒做話說你那是什麼打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們兩個孤男寡女的去了哪裡喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 你們到底跑哪裡去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 這怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只不過我們兩個女孩子開了個小會而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:19:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月學姐 我親~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在做什麼呢 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那海人也來一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗喵和美櫻喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們倆跑去哪了喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 你們都跑哪裡去了喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}過分過分！只留下我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好睏…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能在這裡睡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這到底什麼情況！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你竟然為了保護我而…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}CUT
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣一來樹下的戲份就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}攝影結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:20:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼我因為要趕飛機 就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思啊 讓你拖到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍攝要加油啊 完成之後一定要讓我看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樹下同學 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再這麼呆頭呆腦的 我就把小海搶走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}寂寞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 有一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}畢竟是初戀情人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們是傍晚的班機來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是下午五點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天的攝影到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}東西收好以後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就好好享受沖繩的大海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:21:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…對海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}北原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.95,0:23:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬說要大家一起去逛廟會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.46,0:23:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那真是太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}散發著陰謀的氣息啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
